{"tid":229392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又一傻仔公然犯法","createTime":"2017-05-04T14:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T08:51:21.000Z","uid":39305,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3a24f01ee0e5fcb1f208edfcab7fa3f5637dce","tid":229392,"uid":39305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qPg78LG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqPg78LG.jpg&h=1615f3a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係人都知伸縮警棍係違禁品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n伸縮警棍受《武器條例》監管，列為違禁武器，同受監管的違禁武器包括中國式飛鏢、彈簧鋼棒及附有手柄鐵鏈等。根據有關法例，在本港伸縮警棍只配給執法人員使用，其他人士藏有或使用伸縮警棍均屬違法，最高刑罰為罰款一萬元及入獄三年。<br />\n警方警告根據法例精神，愛好收藏武器的武器迷及出售這些違禁武器的人士均已觸犯法例。<br />\n<br />\n大家記得唔好買！"},{"pid":"ad1809d0b6272ca082b56409f11a53bd9e9f5941","tid":229392,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:38:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ad96c834e703867bb4930511c570f9da420b27a","tid":229392,"uid":39305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:43:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ching係咪5毛<br />\n出廢post洗走郭文貴post?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfaa21a662f42eb309e5f5dde2ae27d6f81ebcba","tid":229392,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:47:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ching係咪5毛<br />\n出廢post洗走郭文貴post?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呢幾日開post回post嘅，都係5毛<br />\n只可以講郭文貴"},{"pid":"766e1262e8e9a874d66c23ce5cc145d52afae6ad","tid":229392,"uid":39305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>ching係咪5毛<br />\n出廢post洗走郭文貴post?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquo